text: Stefan Nutz (born 15 February 1992) is an Austrian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Austrian Bundesliga club SV Ried. ==Career== Stefan Nutz started playing football for FC Pöls. Other youth teamswere SK Sturm Graz and GAK. 2010 he started his professional career with the first team of GAK. 2012 he joined SV Grödig in the Second league. Withe the team he was promoted to the Bundesliga. 2015 he went to SK Rapid Wien. In August 2017 he joined SV Ried. After the relegation he went on to SCR Altach. On 7 July 2019 Nutz he went back to Ried.
